description: Parameterized test, which creates issues of all possible types and assigns them to current user

steps.name: Click "JIRA project" button on the start page
Click "Create" button in header the JIRA project page
Open issue types list on Create issue modal
Select issue type on Create issue modal
Fill issue summary on Create issue modal
Fill issue description on Create issue modal

parameters.name: text
parameters.value: Test description for testing description field for type Task

steps.name: Click "Assign to me" button on Create issue modal
